<ng-container [ngSwitch]="variant">
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.elevated" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'rounded-none': rounded === roundedV.none,
            'rounded-sm': rounded === roundedV.sm,
            'rounded-md': rounded === roundedV.md,
            'rounded-lg': rounded === roundedV.lg,
            'rounded-full': rounded === roundedV.full,
            'shadow-sm shadow-neutral-400': true,
            'px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs text-nowrap font-semibold bg-green-600 text-green-800 bg-opacity-10 hover:bg-opacity-15': btnV.elevated,
            }">
            <!-- <ng-content select="nxt-button"></ng-content> -->
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.filled" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'rounded-none': rounded === roundedV.none,
            'rounded-sm': rounded === roundedV.sm,
            'rounded-md': rounded === roundedV.md,
            'rounded-lg': rounded === roundedV.lg,
            'rounded-full': rounded === roundedV.full,
            'px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs text-nowrap font-semibold bg-green-800 text-green-100': btnV.filled,
            }">
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.filledTonal" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'rounded-none': rounded === roundedV.none,
            'rounded-sm': rounded === roundedV.sm,
            'rounded-md': rounded === roundedV.md,
            'rounded-lg': rounded === roundedV.lg,
            'rounded-full': rounded === roundedV.full,
            'px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs text-nowrap font-semibold bg-orange-600 bg-opacity-15 text-green-900': btnV.filledTonal,
            }">
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.outlined" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'rounded-none': rounded === roundedV.none,
            'rounded-sm': rounded === roundedV.sm,
            'rounded-md': rounded === roundedV.md,
            'rounded-lg': rounded === roundedV.lg,
            'rounded-full': rounded === roundedV.full,
            'px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs text-nowrap font-semibold bg-transparent border-green-800 border text-green-800': btnV.outlined,
            }">
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.text" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-nowrap bg-transparent text-green-800': btnV.text,
            }">
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.icon" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-nowrap bg-transparent text-green-800': btnV.icon,
            }">
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.segmented" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'rounded-none': rounded === roundedV.none,
            'rounded-sm': rounded === roundedV.sm,
            'rounded-md': rounded === roundedV.md,
            'rounded-lg': rounded === roundedV.lg,
            'rounded-full': rounded === roundedV.full,
            'px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs text-nowrap font-semibold bg-orange-600 bg-opacity-15 text-green-900': true,
            }">
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.fab" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'rounded-none': rounded === roundedV.none,
            'rounded-sm': rounded === roundedV.sm,
            'rounded-md': rounded === roundedV.md,
            'rounded-lg': rounded === roundedV.lg,
            'rounded-full': rounded === roundedV.full,
            'shadow-md shadow-neutral-400': true,
            'p-4 text-xs text-nowrap font-semibold bg-green-500 text-green-950 bg-opacity-20 hover:bg-opacity-15': true,
            }">
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template *ngSwitchCase="btnV.extendedFab" #default [ngTemplateOutlet]="customTemplate || default">
        <button href="#" [ngClass]="customStyle || {
            'rounded-none': rounded === roundedV.none,
            'rounded-sm': rounded === roundedV.sm,
            'rounded-md': rounded === roundedV.md,
            'rounded-lg': rounded === roundedV.lg,
            'rounded-full': rounded === roundedV.full,
            'shadow-sm shadow-neutral-400': true,
            'p-3 text-xs text-nowrap font-semibold bg-green-500 text-green-950 bg-opacity-20 hover:bg-opacity-15': true,
            }">
            <ng-container [ngTemplateOutlet]="content"></ng-container>
        </button>
    </ng-template>
</ng-container>

<ng-template #content>
    <ng-content></ng-content>
</ng-template>
